Day 66: Deploy MySQL on Kubernetes

Date: November 2, 2025
Overview
Set up MySQL database with proper storage and configuration.
Key Concepts Learned

Stateful application deployment
Database initialization
Secret management for credentials
Backup considerations

Commands Used
yamlapiVersion: apps/v1
kind: StatefulSet
metadata:
  name: mysql
spec:
  serviceName: mysql
  replicas: 1
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: mysql
        image: mysql:5.7
        env:
        - name: MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD
          valueFrom:
            secretKeyRef:
              name: mysql-secret
              key: password
Challenges Faced
StatefulSets are complex! Understanding ordering guarantees and persistent volume claims per pod.
